# Estate Identity Rule

**Manifest (single source of truth):** `docs/estate/ESTATE_PLACE_MASTER_MANIFEST.json`  
**Protocol:** `docs/estate/ESTATE_PLACE_MASTER_MANIFEST_PROTOCOL.md`  
**Room registry:** `docs/estate/ESTATE_ROOM_REGISTRY.json` Â· `lib/estate/estateRoomAliasCatalog.ts`  
**Regenerate:** `node scripts/generate-estate-place-master-manifest.mjs`

## Binding rule

A room name must **never** route to:

- an app feature
- a settings page
- an audio category
- a similar-looking room
- a temporary image substitute

Every physical Estate destination has **one permanent `ESTATE-ROOM` id**.

Descriptions and aliases may vary. **The destination does not.**

