## When adding or editing estate navigation

1. Assign or reuse a semantic `ESTATE-ROOM-*` id in the registry generator.
2. Set `primary_owner` on images â€” never borrow greenhouse for gardens/orchard.
3. Add `avoid_confusion_with` for look-alike rooms.
4. Add `disallowed_aliases` so cross-room phrases do not steal navigation.
5. Removed rooms: set `navigable: false`, `merged_into_place_id`, and `PLACE_ID_ALIASES` redirect.
